<plot>16-year-old Fidel Castro loves America. He even hopes to reach Hollywood one day and become a star like his hero, Clark Gable. When Fidel goes on a double date he is instantly taken by Sally, a stunning beauty visiting from California. But when 25-year-old John F. Kennedy struts into the bar with a couple of other U.S. Navy soldiers, Fidel is forced to compete for Sally's attention, and he will never look at America the same way again.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?134156</url></doc>
